      <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0; font-size: 1.75rem; color: #666; 
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Times New Roman', serif;">
      a systems-oriented technologist building in engineering, neuroscience and embodied experience
      </p>

      <div style="height: 1.5rem;"></div>

      <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #666; 
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Times New Roman', serif;">
     co-founder of Agorum, neuroscience/engineering at the University of Pennsylvania.</p>

     <div style="height: 1.5rem;"></div>

      <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #666; 
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Times New Roman', serif;">
     a versatile operator and builder in bioengineering, AI systems and consumer tech.</p>

      <div style="height: 1.5rem;"></div>

     <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #666; 
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Times New Roman', serif;">
     an avid photographer, outdoor athlete and music enthusiast. </p>


    
      <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
        x: <a href="https://x.com/Jerber2001" style="color: #444; text-decoration: underline;">@jerber2001</a> |
